data.description: This beautiful home sits just outside city limits of Vidalia on double lot. The great room with engineered hardwood floors is oversized with the fully equipped kitchen overlooking the large living area and breakfast nook with views to the backyard and sunroom. There is a formal dining room and pantry. Split plan with master suite on one end with walk-in closet, jetted tub and separate shower. There are two nice sized bedrooms and a full bath on the other side of great room. A large laundry room sits in hall just inside from the 2-car garage. The 4th bedroom sits above the garage area. Off of the sunroom with heat/ac, there is a large, covered patio. BONUS: large multi-use building with full bath in back which would be a great guest suite or pool house. It has a workshop with roll-up doors on the back side. The kids will love the playhouse which sits high and overlooks the yard. With this much room, a pool and garden are both options. Call Mary today to view at 912-326-1575.
